title: Young Man with a Horn [1950]
description:
Young Man with a Horn [1950]
112 min, Black & White

Kirk Douglas as Rick Martin 
Lauren Bacall as Amy North 
Doris Day as Jo Jordan 
Hoagy Carmichael as Willie &#039;Smoke&#039; Willoughby 
Juano Hernandez as Art Hazzard 

Featuring the golden trumpet of Harry James

As a boy, orphan and dropout Rick Martin finds his only outlet in music. Through chance-met black jazzman Art Hazzard, he develops into a great trumpeter...too great for jazz-hating Jack Chandler, leader of the dance band he joins. But before long he&#039;s in a better big band, thanks to the interest of sweet singer Jo Jordan, who alas introduces him to her slinky, rich, highly neurotic friend Amy North. Amy&#039;s inconsistent ways soon make Rick a virtual basket case. Is he washed up, or will he find that elusive high note his trumpet won&#039;t play? Based on the life of jazz great Bix Beiderbecke.
